2172
01:53:19,875 --> 01:53:20,500
Trains!?

2173
01:53:20,500 --> 01:53:22,917
Oh! So that's in pipeline too

2174
01:53:22,958 --> 01:53:25,250
We're investing 500
crores in this project

2175
