also got permission
from the Collector.

2205
01:54:50,500 --> 01:54:51,917
-Shall we protest?
-We will protest!

2206
01:54:51,917 --> 01:54:54,000
-Shall we protest?
-We will protest!

2207
01:54:54,042 --> 01:54:56,167
So I sent two of my
men into the crowd

2208
01:55:00,167 --> 01:55:02,167
You got the permission
from the collector

2209
01:55:03,167 --> 01:55:04,375
I was left with no choice

2210
01:55:04,833 --> 01:55:07,833
