you people dug as their graves.

2211
01:55:13,750 --> 01:55:15,417
Man-made Landslide!

2212
01:55:15,500 --> 01:55:17,875
For public it seemed like
a natural Landslide.

2213
01:55:17,917 --> 01:55:20,167
