01:57:08,083 --> 01:57:08,625
Hey!

2235
01:57:12,083 --> 01:57:13,083
Shakthi!

2236
01:58:20,542 --> 01:58:22,125
Die damn it!

2237
01:59:26,583 --> 01:59:28,000
Ah...Shit!

2238
02:00:02,958 --> 02:00:03,917
Maya!

2239
02:00:05,667 --> 02:00:09,250
