you're right.

2275
02:03:18,917 --> 02:03:20,208
Police - 1 Lac

2276
02:03:20,708 --> 02:03:22,167
PWD officer - 3 Lacs

2277
02:03:22,167 --> 02:03:23,750
and Councilor - 10 Lacs

2278
02:03:24,417 --> 02:03:26,750
Just for the sake of money

2279
02:03:26,750 --> 02:03:29,750
