2282
02:03:33,333 --> 02:03:35,958
He gave me a new
life with a new face

2283
02:03:38,000 --> 02:03:39,500
What can I do for him?

2284
02:03:42,958 --> 02:03:44,292
Shiva, I've read in a novel

2285
02:03:44,333 --> 02:03:47,917
If Epidefrine is induced into
